# jn:19:26 فلما رأى يسوع امه والتلميذ الذي كان يحبه واقفا قال لامه يا
~~امرأة هوذا ابنك standing by the cross of jesus were his mother and his
~~mother's sister, mary the wife of clopas, and mary of magdala when jesus
~~saw his mother 11 and the disciple there whom he loved, he said to his
